康民, 花名[肥田廖]大陸沙嘴叫雞,竟然在祖國晒委任證求俾面判刑15 天,大陸公安直言冇面俾.<br />\n <br />\n5. [紫藤]組織發起遊行，抗議警方藉放蛇多次免費享用嫖妓，口爆及手淫等服務，港大法律系副授楊艾文指警方無此需要。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1nXu5QYP9N-defZrSlvWtbaFa8DZWkfOPlkn2BWUx4NQ/mobilebasic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1nXu5QYP9N-defZrSlvWtbaFa8DZWkfOPlkn2BWUx4NQ%2Fmobilebasic&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3f5af691\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1nXu5QYP9N-defZrSlvWtbaFa8DZWkfOPlkn2BWUx4NQ/mobilebasic</a>"}]}